{"id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0005","text":"爲何沒有他可痛不欲生","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的極端","失落與痛苦"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["痛不欲生","爲何"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,3,9,4,3,2,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ho4","mut6","jau5","taa1","ho2","tung3","bat1","juk6","sang1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"爲何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"沒有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"他","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"痛不欲生","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"再次以疑問句開頭，質疑為何沒有對方（他）的陪伴，自己就無法承受極度的痛苦。"},"source":{"title":"衆傷","artists":["孫耀威"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5330","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0006","text":"未曾識他卻懂做人","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的理解","人際關係"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["識","做人"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,0,3,3,4,9,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mei6","cang4","sik1","taa1","koek3","dung2","zou6","jan4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"未曾","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"識","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"他","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"卻","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"懂","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"做人","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"對比「痛不欲生」的強烈情感，提出即使不認識對方，卻似乎懂得如何與人相處的諷刺。"},"source":{"title":"衆傷","artists":["孫耀威"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5330","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
