{"id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0009","text":"真的得你嗎 得你是人吧","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的獨特性","孤獨感"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["得你","人"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,5,3,3,5,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zan1","dik1","dak1","nei5","maa1","dak1","nei5","si6","jan4","baa6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"真的","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"嗎","pos":"PART"},{"text":"得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"吧","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"以反問句質疑對方是否是唯一一個有如此情感的人，帶有孤獨和不被理解的感覺。"},"source":{"title":"衆傷","artists":["孫耀威"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5330","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0010","text":"舍不了代價還是氣難下","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的取捨","無奈與掙扎"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["舍不了","代價","氣難下"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,3,5,2,4,0,2,4,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["se2","bat1","liu5","doi6","gaa3","waan4","si6","hei3","naan4","haa6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"舍","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不了","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"代價","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"還是","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"氣難","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"下","pos":"ADV"}],"syntax_notes":"表達在情感關係中，即使無法放下，也因為付出的代價而感到無奈和難以承受。"},"source":{"title":"衆傷","artists":["孫耀威"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5330","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5a2Z6ICA5aiB_NTMzMA_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
